Phn tch danh mc

by Samuel Ching, Maxwell Margenot, Gus Gordon, and Delaney Mackenzie

Edited by AI Cafe

Trong quy trnh lm vic chuyn nghip ca cc nh nh lng, vic chng minh hiu qu ca bt k danh mc u t no thng qua vic kim tra cht ch l rt quan trng. iu ny l c s hiu r v h s ri ro cng nh hiu sut ca danh mc u t.

Vn vi Backtesting

Thng th c xu hng chy nhiu backtest trong qu trnh xy dng mt thut ton. Mt cm by ph bin l s dng thnh cng ca cc backtest nh mt tiu ch phn hi tinh chnh cc tham s hoc c im ca thut ton trong khi vn ang giai on xy dng. iu ny dn n vic qu khp chin lc vi cc thi k m ngi dng thc hin cc backtest. Cui cng, iu ny dn n hiu sut km khi trin khai ra ngoi mu trong giao dch trc tip.

Do , vic chy cc backtest v to ra cc tearsheet ch nn xy ra giai on cui ca vng i to ra thut ton. Chng ta s c c bc tranh v hiu sut ca thut ton, gip ngi dng quyt nh xem c nn tip tc trin khai thut ton hay chuyn sang mt chin lc khc.

C hai phn chnh trong mt tearsheet pyfolio y . u tin, c cc thng k hiu sut nh dng bng. Cc ch s hu ch nh t sut sinh li hng nm, beta th trng v t l Sharpe u c lit k trong bng ny. Nhng ch s ny khng ch i din cho vic chin lc hot ng tt nh th no trong thi gian ca backtest (t l sinh li hng nm), m cn cho thy t sut sinh li iu chnh theo ri ro c o bng cc t l khc nhau. Chng ta s i vo chi tit hn v ngha ca nhng ch s ny.

Tip theo, c cc biu gip hnh dung nhiu loi ch s hiu sut. V d, ngi dng c th s dng cc biu gim gi nhanh chng xc nh cc thi k m chin lc hot ng km nht. Ngoi ra, n s gip ngi dng thy liu chin lc c hot ng nh mong i hay khng - nu mt chin lc khng b nh hng bi th trng nhng li gp phi cc t gim gi ln trong cc giai on khng hong, th r rng c vn vi thit k hoc trin khai ca chin lc .

Ci t danh mc phn tch

Gi s chng ta xy dng mt danh mc c phiu bao gm FPT, HPG, VCB theo phng php chia u vn v chn VNINDEX lm benchmark

In[3]:
# Ci th vin ly d liu min ph
!curl -fsSLO https://raw.githubusercontent.com/algo-stocks/data/master/data.py
In[4]:
from data import get_prices

start = '2024-01-01'
end = '2025-01-01'

closes = get_prices('FPT', 'HPG', 'VCB', 'VNINDEX', start_date=start, end_date=end)

benchmark_rets = closes['VNINDEX'].ffill().pct_change().dropna()
bt_returns = closes.drop('VNINDEX', axis=1).pct_change().mean(axis=1).dropna()

By gi, chng ta sn sng s dng pyfolio khm ph cc ch s hiu sut v th khc nhau ca thut ton ca chng ta. Trong sut bi ging ny, chng ta s chi tit cch din gii cc th ring khc nhau c to ra bi pyfolio v bao gm lnh thch hp to ton b bo co.

Thng k Hiu sut

Vi pyfolio, c rt nhiu thng k hiu sut m hu ht cc nh qun l qu chuyn nghip s s dng phn tch hiu sut ca thut ton. Cc ch s ny bao gm li nhun hng nm v hng thng ca thut ton, cc phn v li nhun, beta cun v t l Sharpe n doanh thu ca danh mc u t. Cc ch s quan trng nht s c tho lun nh sau.

Li nhun iu chnh theo ri ro

Li nhun iu chnh theo ri ro l mt ch s quan trng ca bt k chin lc no. Li nhun iu chnh theo ri ro cho php chng ta nh gi cc dng li nhun c bin ng ring l khc nhau bng cch cung cp mt phng tin so snh c ngha. C nhiu cch o lng li nhun iu chnh theo ri ro, nhng mt trong nhng ch s ph bin nht l t l Sharpe.

In[5]:
print("The Sharpe Ratio of the backtest is: ", empyrical.sharpe_ratio(bt_returns))

The Sharpe Ratio of the backtest is:  1.865096570100442

Beta Th Trng

Beta th trng ca mt thut ton l mc tip xc ca chin lc vi th trng rng ln hn. V d, beta th trng bng $1$ c ngha l bn ang mua vo th trng, trong khi beta bng $-1$ c ngha l bn ang bn khng th trng. Bt k beta no trong khong ny cho thy nh hng ca th trng c gim bt, trong khi bt k beta no ngoi khong ny cho thy nh hng ca th trng c tng cng.

In[6]:
print("The market beta of the backtest is: ", empyrical.beta(bt_returns,benchmark_rets))

The market beta of the backtest is:  0.9207793387536886

Drawdowns

Drawdowns l s 'st gim t nh n y' ca mt chin lc u t. Ni mt cch trc quan, n cp n nhng tn tht m chin lc tri qua t s vn c bn m n c nh. V d, trong cuc Khng hong Ti chnh 2008, mc gim st ca th trng l hn 50% t nh nm 2007 n y nm 2009.

In[7]:
print("The maxmimum drawdown of the backtest is: ", empyrical.max_drawdown(bt_returns))

The maxmimum drawdown of the backtest is:  -0.08591775202527228

y l mt thc o khc v ri ro ti chnh ca mt thut ton. Nu mc gim rng ca mt chin lc l rt ng k, iu ny thng c ngha l bin ng ca thut ton cng ln hn. Cc chin lc tt c gng hn ch mc gim. Mt tiu chun tt l c mc gim ti a di 20%.

Plotting

Trong pyfolio, c mt module plotting cho php ngi dng nhanh chng v cc ch s ny.

Biu Li nhun

Cc biu v li nhun tch ly v li nhun hng ngy khng tch ly gip bn c ci nhn nhanh chng v hiu sut ca thut ton v pht hin bt k s bt thng no trong khong thi gian backtest. Biu li nhun tch ly cng cho php bn so snh vi li nhun tham chiu - iu ny c th so snh vi mt chin lc u t khc hoc mt ch s nh VNINDEX.

In[8]:
# Cumulative Returns
plt.subplot(2,1,1)
pf.plotting.plot_rolling_returns(bt_returns, benchmark_rets)

# Daily, Non-Cumulative Returns
plt.subplot(2,1,2)
pf.plotting.plot_returns(bt_returns)
plt.tight_layout()

Vi cc biu li nhun hng nm v hng thng, bn c th thy nhng nm v thng m thut ton hot ng tt nht. V d, trong biu nhit hng thng, thut ton ny hot ng tt nht vo thng 2 nm 2024 (c t mu xanh m). Trong mt bi backtest vi khong thi gian di hn, cc biu ny s tit l nhiu thng tin hn. Hn na, s phn b ca li nhun hng thng cng rt hu ch trong vic nh gi cch m thut ton hot ng trong cc giai on khc nhau trong nm v xem n c b nh hng bi cc khun mu ma v hay khng.

In[9]:
fig = plt.figure(1)
plt.subplot(1,3,1)
pf.plot_annual_returns(bt_returns)
plt.subplot(1,3,2)
pf.plot_monthly_returns_dist(bt_returns)
plt.subplot(1,3,3)
pf.plot_monthly_returns_heatmap(bt_returns)
plt.tight_layout()
fig.set_size_inches(15,5)

Cc T Phn Li Nhun

Cc biu hp v ru ny cung cp ci nhn tng quan v cc t phn li nhun c phn chia theo khung thi gian li nhun (hng ngy / hng tun / hng thng) trong ton b khong thi gian backtest.

In[10]:
pf.plot_return_quantiles(bt_returns);

ng trung tm gia mi hp cho thy li nhun trung v, v hp cho thy t phn th nht (percentile 25) cng nh t phn th ba (percentile 75). Trong khi li nhun trung v cao lun hu ch, vic hiu r phn phi li nhun cng quan trng khng km. Mt hp cht ch c ngha l phn ln li nhun (t percentile 25 n 75) nm trong mt gii hn hp - tc l li nhun n nh v khng bin ng ln. Mt hp ln hn c ngha l li nhun phn tn hn. Tuy nhin, iu quan trng l phi ch n thang o bn tri t cc t phn vo ng bi cnh. Ngoi ra, li nhun trong cc khong thi gian di hn s c phn phi rng hn v vic tng di thi gian lm tng tnh bin ng ca li nhun.

"Cc si tua" cui ch ra nhng li nhun nm ngoi percentile 25 v 75. Mt hp cht ch vi cc si tua di cho thy c th c nhng gi tr ngoi lai trong li nhun - iu ny c th khng l tng nu cc gi tr ngoi lai l tiu cc. iu ny c th cho thy chin lc ca bn c th nhy cm vi mt s iu kin th trng / khong thi gian nht nh.

Biu ng

Di y, chng ta c mt s biu ng cho thy cch c tnh thay i trong sut thi gian kim tra li. Trong trng hp ca beta ng v t l Sharpe ng, c tnh ng cung cp cho chng ta nhiu thng tin hn so vi c tnh im n trong ton b thi gian. Mt c tnh ng cho php ngi dng thy liu li nhun iu chnh theo ri ro ca thut ton (t l Sharpe) c n nh theo thi gian hay khng, hoc liu n c dao ng ng k khng. Mt t l Sharpe bin ng c th cho thy rng chin lc c th ri ro hn vo nhng thi im nht nh hoc rng n khng hot ng tt vo nhng thi im ny. Tng t, mt beta bin ng cho thy rng n chu nh hng t th trng vo nhng thi im nht nh - nu chin lc c thit k trung lp vi th trng, iu ny c th l mt du hiu cnh bo.

Biu Beta ng

Biu di y cho thy beta ng ca chin lc so vi li nhun chun trong ton b thi gian ca bi th nghim. Trong trng hp ny, li nhun chun ca VNINDEX c s dng. V vy, beta danh mc ng cng thp so vi VNINDEX, thut ton cng trung tnh vi th trng.

In[11]:
pf.plot_rolling_beta(bt_returns, benchmark_rets);

Biu T l Sharpe ng

Biu di y cho thy t l Sharpe ng trong khong thi gian backtest. iu ny gip bn hiu c hiu sut ca thut ton ti cc thi im khc nhau.

In[12]:
pf.plot_rolling_sharpe(bt_returns);

Biu Gim Gi

Trong biu ny, chng ta s trc quan ha biu gim gi c m t trn. Biu ny cung cp ci nhn tng quan v cc khong thi gian gim gi ti t nht trong qu trnh backtest. Nhng khong thi gian ny cho thy cc khung thi gian trong qu trnh kim tra li m 10 khong gim gi ln nht xy ra.

In[13]:
pf.plot_drawdown_periods(bt_returns);

iu ny, kt hp vi biu underwater, cho php kim tra nhanh vo cc thi k m thut ton gp kh khn. Ni chung, cng t bin ng th thut ton cng c xu hng gim thiu c cc t gim gi.

In[14]:
pf.plot_drawdown_underwater(bt_returns);
